New Feature Release: Dark Mode & Performance Improvements

Hi everyone,

We're excited to announce the latest update to Meeru!

What's New:
- Dark Mode: Easy on the eyes during late-night email sessions
- 50% faster email loading
- Improved search with instant results
- Better attachment handling

Try it out and let us know what you think!

The Meeru Team
https://meeru.app/changelog

